# Ransomware Detector v2 — Runtime Dependencies (loose specs / source of truth)
#
# This is the human-edited input file. The pinned `requirements.txt` is
# either generated from this file via:
#
#     pip install pip-tools
#     pip-compile --output-file=requirements.txt --strip-extras requirements.in
#
# or — when pip-compile is not available — written by hand using the same
# top-level pins via the PEP 440 compatible-release operator (`~=`) so we
# accept patch-level upgrades but never breaking minor/major bumps.

